{
  "texts": [
    "For instance, a locally hosted LLM might be granted access to patient-specific data.",
    "This data can be integrated into a tailored prompt designed to identify the most appropriate treatment plan for a specific patient.",
    "The LLM, will have contemporary access to the guidelines and provide a recommendation on treatment based on guideline knowledge.",
    "However, before having LLM-aided CDSSs, it is necessary to define the best guidelines format that can maximize output accuracy.",
    "We demonstrate the performance of our proposed framework in a subset of the potential questions that could be asked by physicians managing patients with chronic HCV."
  ]
}